 interest in improving Shopify's security. We look forward to more reports from you!","markdown_message":"\u003cp\u003eHello \u003ca href=\"/tems\"\u003e@tems\u003c/a\u003e, thanks for the added information! The new bypass you are describing is from the same root cause as the initial issue. Once the application is open, after the first activity, it won\u0026#39;t show the biometrics prompt again. In the case of a deeplink multiple activities are shown so the prompt is bypassed. We\u0026#39;re rolling out a fix in version 8.27.0 today which fixes the root cause so it should fix both issues.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWe have determined that the initial bounty amount is appropriate for this report. This report may also be eligible for the Google Play Security Rewards Program, please see \u003ca title=\"https://hackerone.com/googleplay\" href=\"https://hackerone.com/googleplay\"\u003ehttps://hackerone.com/googleplay\u003c/a\u003e for more details.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThank you for your interest in improving Shopify\u0026#39;s security. We look forward to more reports from you!\u003c/p\u003e\n","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2019-07-30T21:17:39.394Z","updated_at":"2019-07-30T21:17:39.394Z","actor":{"username":"michael_hughes","cleared":false,"url":"/michael_hughes","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"/assets/avatars/default-71a302d706457f3d3a31eb30fa3e73e6cf0b1d677b8fa218eaeaffd67ae97918.png"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":null},"reporter":{"username":"tems","url":"/tems"},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"shopify","actor_is_team_member":true,"actor_is_concealed_member":false},{"id":5470763,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::AgreedOnGoingPublic","message":"","markdown_message":"","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2019-07-31T13:47:30.380Z","updated_at":"2019-07-31T13:47:30.380Z","first_to_agree":true,"actor":{"username":"michael_hughes","cleared":false,"url":"/michael_hughes","profile_picture_urls